            "body": [
                {
                    "sentence_categories": [],
                    "sentence_skills": [],
                    "text": "Yeah, it belongs alone for now  we can hopefully add Add Annotation soon.",
                    "_notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "sentence_categories": [],
                    "sentence_skills": [],
                    "text": "Also, if you have the original icon you used for that, you can remove the Z. I'm not sure why we have Z overlays at all for these, given that they're now all within a dedicated Zotero tab (or is there a way to add them to some quick-access toolbar where they'd be out of context?).",
                    "_notes": ""
                },
                {
                    "sentence_categories": [],
                    "sentence_skills": [],
                    "text": "For the tab, what is Z taken by?",
                    "_notes": ""
                }
            ],
            "_notes": "",
            "created_at": "2023-03-02 20:50:21",
            "updated_at": "2023-03-02 20:50:21"
